metadata.name: La Merxhe
metadata.description:
Created with machine learning, she would have to be a woman who enjoys movement. I could also say that she is my alter ego. A marked event in the history of cryptocurrency represented on a B&W canvas with an abstract style, voluminous, soft textures, skin, body.  
What would be the face of a Mexican, dancer, that in her represents the history of contemporary & modern dance?

Collaboration with Stable Diffusion + Aiva + Videopad.
